```python id=bloq
from qualtran.bloqs.mcmt import MultiControlX
bloq = MultiControlX(cvs=(1,) * 12)
```
```python id=golden
import numpy as np
# c12x: control=first 12 qubits (MSB), target=last (big-endian).
golden = np.zeros((1<<13, 1<<13), dtype=complex)
for s in range(1<<13):
    o = (s ^ 1) if (s >> 1) == ((1<<12) - 1) else s
    golden[o, s] = 1
```
